@using (Ajax.BeginForm("BookIssueReturnEdit", "Library", new { controller = "Library" }, new AjaxOptions { HttpMethod = "Post", OnSuccess = "successEdit" }, new { @class = "form-horizontal from-custom online-form", id = "form-id" }))
{<div class="lag">
    <span class="stack">
        <label class="label-90">
            Type</label>
        <span class="field">@Html.DropDownListFor(m => m.BookIssueReturn.Type, Model.BookIssueReturn.Typelist, new { @class = "input-100 input", entermsg = "Enter Type" })
